pplications</span></h3></section><section class="flex justify-center" data-v-ba716fcb><div class="max-w-screen-xl lg:flex lg:flex-wrap lg:justify-around xl:mt-6 xl:px-8" data-v-ba716fcb><!--[--><div class="flex first:mt-0 mt-10 w-full max-w-md lg:flex-col lg:p-5 lg:w-1/3" data-v-ba716fcb><div class="mr-4 lg:mr-0" data-v-ba716fcb><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.455" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 text-teal-400 xl:h-8" data-v-ba716fcb><path d="M8.727 16.727H5.455c-1.095.001-2.15-.41-2.956-1.15a4.36 4.36 0 0 1-1.396-2.848c-.091-1.09.23-2.177.902-3.041A4.37 4.37 0 0 1 4.727 8.06V8C4.727 3.983 7.983.727 12 .727S19.273 3.983 19.273 8v.06c1.076.185 2.044.767 2.712 1.631a4.37 4.37 0 0 1 .897 3.036c-.091 1.089-.587 2.103-1.39 2.844a4.36 4.36 0 0 1-2.947 1.156h-3.273m-7.636-4.363L12 8m0 0l4.364 4.364M12 8v14.546"></path></svg></div><div class="lg:mt-7" data-v-ba716fcb><h4 class="text-gray-800 text-sm font-semibold lg:text-lg xl:text-xl" data-v-ba716fcb>Cutting Edge</h4><p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-xs leading-normal lg:text-sm xl:text-base" data-v-ba716fcb>We install Nginx, PHP, MySQL, Postgres, Redis, and all of the other goodies you need on the cloud of your choice. No more out-dated PHP installations.</p><a class="inline-block mt-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-teal-400 font-semibold" href="docs/1.0/introduction.html" data-v-ba716fcb>Learn more ›</a></div></div><div class="flex first:mt-0 mt-10 w-full max-w-md lg:flex-col lg:p-5 lg:w-1/3" data-v-ba716fcb><div class="mr-4 lg:mr-0" data-v-ba716fcb><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 text-teal-400 xl:h-8" data-v-ba716fcb><path d="M11 15L31 7V23L11 31V15Z"></path><path d="M6.907 23.037L1 25V9L21 1V7" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg></div><div class="lg:mt-7" data-v-ba716fcb><h4 class="text-gray-800 text-sm font-semibold lg:text-lg xl:text-xl" data-v-ba716fcb>Push To Deploy</h4><p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-xs leading-normal lg:text-sm xl:text-base" data-v-ba716fcb>Deploying code couldn&#39;t be any easier. Just push to master on your GitHub, Bitbucket, or custom Git repository. We&#39;ll handle it from there.</p><a class="inline-block mt-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-teal-400 font-semibold" href="docs/1.0/sites/deployments.html#quick-deploy" data-v-ba716fcb>Learn more ›</a></div></div><div class="flex first:mt-0 mt-10 w-full max-w-md lg:flex-col lg:p-5 lg:w-1/3" data-v-ba716fcb><div class="mr-4 lg:mr-0" data-v-ba716fcb><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 text-teal-400 xl:h-8" data-v-ba716fcb><path d="M16 31H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V13a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h18a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v1M5 11V8a7 7 0 0 1 7-7 7 7 0 0 1 7 7" stroke-linecap="round"></path><path d="M24 31a7 7 0 0 0 4.95-2.05A7 7 0 0 0 31 24a7 7 0 0 0-2.05-4.95A7 7 0 0 0 24 17a7 7 0 0 0-7 7 7 7 0 0 0 7 7h0z"></path><path d="M21 24l2 2 4-4" stroke-linecap="round"></path></svg></div><div class="lg:mt-7" data-v-ba716fcb><h4 class="text-gray-800 text-sm font-semibold lg:text-lg xl:text-xl" data-v-ba716fcb>Free TLS Certificates</h4><p class="mt-2 text-gray-600 text-xs leading-normal lg:text-sm xl:text-base" data-v-ba716fcb>Forge integrates with LetsEncrypt, allowing you to obtain free TLS (SSL) certificates for your Forge powered applications.</p><a class="inline-block mt-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-teal-400 font-semibold" href="docs/1.0/sites/ssl.html" data-v-ba716fcb>Learn more ›</a></div></div><div class="flex first:mt-0 mt-10 w-full max-w-md lg:flex-col lg:p-5 lg:w-1/3" data-v-ba716fcb><div class="mr-4 lg:mr-0" data-v-ba716fcb><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-6 text-teal-400 xl:h-8" data-v-ba716fcb><path d="M16 21a5 5 0 0 0 5